text: Lucy Punch (born 30 December 1977) is an English actress. She is known for her roles in Ella Enchanted, Hot Fuzz, You Will Meet a Tall Dark Stranger, Dinner for Schmucks, and Into the Woods. ==References== Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:English movie actors Category:English television actors Category:English stage actors Category:English voice actors Category:Actors from London
